==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Marmottes oil
<hw>Mar"mottes oil`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A fine oil obtained from the
kernel of <spn>Prunus brigantiaca</spn>. It is used instead of olive or
almond oil.</def> <rj><au>De Colange.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Marmozet</ent>⟦br⟧
